{
  "stem": "14737.7",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What does it mean, this reparation?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Can they pay for my family, for my father, for my sister, for my immediate family?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And you know what a family I had.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I don't know how the world will look, but one thing let me tell you.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Why'd all this what happen?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Who were these perpetrators?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "These perpetrators were just plain people like you and you, who went to church on Sunday and had children also.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But in a sense, they were murderers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Were they all murderers?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But how about those who were silent, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] who were not even lookers, who know about it and were silent?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They owe also a lot to their conscience.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Because seeing if someone is being killed and being quiet is not the proper way.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We are humans, all.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "For five years, the world has seen, the pope has seen-- not knew about it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Churchill knew about it, so did Roosevelt knew it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "People were asking to bombard Auschwitz when it was apparent also.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We also allowed our-- to those who were silent-- and believe it or not, I blame a lot of Jews in the United States.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, at that time, maybe they didn't have influence.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Why wasn't at that time America [INAUDIBLE]?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Not that time was America [INAUDIBLE] if its philosophy.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "If 5,000 Jews at that time went to Washington and lay down near the White House and not going away until something.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't say they would have saved all the Jews.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't say that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the world should know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I can give you a lot of examples.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
